        <li><strong class="text-white">Max Loss:</strong> Net debit paid</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">Breakeven:</strong> $950 + net debit</li>
      </ul>

      <p>This captures LLY's upside as the market recognizes it as the specialized AI play with real revenue and defensible moats. The 6-month timeframe gives earnings visibility to prove the thesis.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Bitcoin Put Spreads (Accumulation Strategy)</h3>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
        <li><strong class="text-white">Structure:</strong> Sell $50k puts, buy $45k puts on MSTR or Bitcoin ETFs, 60-90 DTE</li>
